OL,3,CPolice officer filmed 'stamping on
OL,4,Cman's head' at airport
OL,6,FClaire Hannah has the latest on a
OL,7,Fvideo circulating online of a police
OL,8,Fofficer kicking and stamping on a
OL,9,Fman's head in Manchester Airport.
OL,11,FA police force has defended the
OL,12,Factions of an officer caught on camera
OL,13,Fkicking a man before stamping on his
OL,14,Fhead while he was on the floor.
OL,16,FFootage has been widely circulated on
OL,17,Fsocial media of an incident at
OL,18,FManchester Airport on Wednesday 24
OL,19,FJuly.
