OL,3,CPolice officer filmed 'stamping on
OL,4,Cman's head' at airport
OL,6,FThe footage, which lasts for more than
OL,7,F40 seconds, shows a fire arm officer
OL,8,Fkicking and stamping on a man's head.
OL,10,FIt later shows the same officer, who
OL,11,Fwas accompanied by two other officers,
OL,12,Farmed with tasers, striking another
OL,13,Fman on the back of his head.
OL,15,FGreater Manchester Police (GMP)
OL,16,Fconfirmed a female police officer
OL,17,Fsustained a broken nose as three
OL,18,Fofficers were subject to a "violent
OL,19,Fassault" in the incident at Terminal
OL,20,F2, in the run up to the footage being
OL,21,Ftaken.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
