OL,6,FIt also said there had been a risk of
OL,7,Fthe armed officers' "firearms being
OL,8,Ftaken".
OL,10,FIn the footage a male officer can be
OL,11,Fseen aiming a taser at a man as he is
OL,12,Flying on the ground.
OL,14,FOnlookers can then be heard shouting
OL,15,Fbefore the officer kicks and stamps on
OL,16,Fthe man's head.
OL,18,FA person is heard yelling "move back",
OL,19,Fbefore a female officer then appears
OL,20,Fto turn her taser and aim it at other
OL,21,Fpeople.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
