OL,3,CPolice officer filmed 'stamping on
OL,4,Cman's head' at airport
OL,6,FA number of voices can be heard
OL,7,Fpleading "stop kicking people", with
OL,8,Fothers shouting expletives, as a
OL,9,Fnumber of officers surround the man on
OL,10,Fthe ground.
OL,12,FSeconds later, an officer is then seen
OL,13,Fto walk over to another man before
OL,14,Fpointing his taser at him. As he moves
OL,15,Fonto the ground on his knees and with
OL,16,Fhis arms in the air, the officer then
OL,17,Fproceeds to kick him.
OL,19,FFour men had been arrested on
OL,20,Fsuspicion of affray and assault on
OL,21,Femergency service workers.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
