OL,6,FThe clip, shared widely on social
OL,7,Fmedia, has received thousands of views
OL,8,Fonline.
OL,10,FGMP said they have 'acknowledged the
OL,11,Fconcerns' regarding conduct and that
OL,12,Fthe incident is being assessed by the
OL,13,FProfessional Standards Directorate.
OL,15,FIn a statement, the force said:
OL,16,F"Officers were called to reports of an
OL,17,Faltercation between members of the
OL,18,Fpublic in Terminal 2 at Manchester
OL,19,FAirport.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
