OL,6,FHome Secretary minister Diana Johnson
OL,7,Fsaid: "I am aware of disturbing
OL,8,Ffootage from an incident at Manchester
OL,9,FAirport this afternoon and understand
OL,10,Fthe public concern it has prompted. I
OL,11,Fhave asked for a full update from
OL,12,FGreater Manchester Police."
